    "title": "32. Longest Valid Parentheses",
    "question": "<div><p>Given a string containing just the characters <code>'('</code> and <code>')'</code>, find the length of the longest valid (well-formed) parentheses substring.</p>\n\n<p><strong>Example 1:</strong></p>\n\n<pre><strong>Input:</strong> \"(()\"\n<strong>Output:</strong> 2\n<strong>Explanation:</strong> The longest valid parentheses substring is <code>\"()\"</code>\n</pre>\n\n<p><strong>Example 2:</strong></p>\n\n<pre><strong>Input:</strong> \"<code>)()())</code>\"\n<strong>Output:</strong> 4\n<strong>Explanation:</strong> The longest valid parentheses substring is <code>\"()()\"</code>\n</pre>\n</div>"
